metadata.name: GoodBoi | Fresh from the Fabrikator
metadata.description:
**Spotless as the day he was built, wearing his birthday best to celebrate the mk.iii Fabrikator that granted him life.** The Goodest of space-boys.
Our voxel-perfect purple lad.
Goes glowing into that good night. Goodboi. Wielding ambiguous energy that’s perhaps best described as ‘giddy panic’, Goodboi is here to spread lowkey weekend mood, gaze unblinking at anything in front of him, and never answer direct questions about the spectacular rear-glow. The most powerful Silhouette in Cypher Space? Certainly.
A happy accident, fabrikated in the days before Voxos were built? Surely.
Constantly yelling and so be thankful he doesn’t come with audio? Uh.. sure.
